  "title": "Pickup point delivery now available in the UK",
  "urlName": "Pickup-point-delivery-now-available-in-the-UK",
  "url": "https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/Pickup-point-delivery-now-available-in-the-UK",
  "language": "en_GB",
  "lastPublishedDate": "2026-03-06T10:32:39.000Z",
  "topics": [],
  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Starting April 2026, you can offer customers delivery to pickup points across the UK.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Note:</strong> This option is only available with BackShip.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Why offer collection point delivery ?</span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Benefits for your business</span></h3>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Lower shipping costs - £3.39 per label (compared to standard home shipping)</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Fewer failed deliveries - customers don&#39;t need to be home (about 50% fewer failed deliveries than home delivery)</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Higher conversion - about 1 in 4 customers choose pickup points when available</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Fewer incidents - pickup points are more secure (fewer lost or stolen parcels)</span></li></ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">BackShip handles the complexity</span></h3>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Claims management - we handle shipping provider investigations.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Automated pickups - regular scheduled collections from your location.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Fewer address errors - automated tracking with no manual input.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Time savings - focus on sourcing and refurbishing, not logistics.</span></li></ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Coverage &amp; availability</span></h3>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Where: UK to UK deliveries only</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Shipping provider: DPD UK</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Network: 12,000+ pickup locations across the UK</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Max weight: 20 kg per product</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Max dimensions: No 2 sides longer than 120 cm (example: 60 cm × 60 cm × 60 cm)</span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How to set up collection point delivery</span></h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Option 1: I already use BackShip</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Log in to your Back Office.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Go to Shipping settings.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Add a new shipping option: DPD UK Pickup Point.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Save and activate.</span></li></ol>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Option 2: I don&#39;t use BackShip yet</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">First, set up a pickup with the shipping provider:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Go to the Seller Support Center and submit a support request:</span></li></ol>\n<ul><li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Order related? → No</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What does your question concern? → Back Market services</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Which service? → BackShip</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What do you want to do? → Set up a regular pickup</span></li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Label Generation</span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Scenario A: I already use BackShip</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">No changes needed. Keep your current process.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Scenario B: I use an integrator with BackShip API</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">No action needed. Your integrator already supports BackShip.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Integrators with BackShip API:</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">ChannelEngine</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Infiplex</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Linnworks</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sellermania</span></li></ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Scenario C: I use an integrator without the BackShip API</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Action needed: integrate the BackShip API. <a href=\"https://api.backmarket.dev/#/operations/GetDeliveries\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\">More details here</span></a>.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Scenario D: I generate labels manually</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Use the same process as usual.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Customer experience</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How do customers collect their parcels?</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer chooses a Pickup point at checkout and selects a location.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You ship with the generated DPD label.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">DPD delivers to the pickup point.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer gets a QR code by email and SMS.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer shows the QR code at the pickup point to collect the parcel.</span></li></ol>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Pickup deadline:</strong> 7 days. Customers get 2 reminders by email and SMS.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Frequently Asked Questions</span></h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How does this affect my on-time delivery (OTD)?</span></strong><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">No negative impact. OTD is counted when DPD delivers to the pickup point (the first delivery attempt), not when the customer collects it.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How does insurance work?</span></strong><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Optional and the same as standard BackShip insurance:</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">All parcels include basic ad valorem coverage (up to the product value).</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You can add extra coverage if needed.</span></li></ul>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How does billing work?</span></strong><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Same as other BackShip options:</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">£3.39 per label for pickup point delivery.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Invoices are issued monthly.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></li><li><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/How-to-understand-your-BackShip-invoices\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\">Learn more here</span></span></a></li></ul>"
}